                <li>
                    <b>&lt;RibbonIconLabel/&gt;</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>Template Name</b>: RibbonIconLabel</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <b>&lt;RibbonSmallIconLabel/&gt;</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>Template Name</b>: RibbonSmallIconLabel</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </p>
        <p>
            <b>&lt;RibbonIconLabel/&gt;</b> is a container with an icon and a label.
            It only respons to the <b>Small</b> and <b>Icon</b> size in <b>&lt;RibbonButtons/&gt;</b>.
        </p>
        <p>
            The <b>Image</b> property defines the icon.
            Everything put inside this control is displayed to the right side of the label.
        </p>
